lyTime":"2018-04-28T12:10:57.000Z","msg":"立刻叫架二手爛船去繞台一週喇<br />\n厲害了。"},{"pid":"4e59b8e21ef4a4dd783bde9e61686ee3cf278fb8","tid":645262,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bada8645ef42c61196bd6c9f9e28804a1deaac8","tid":645262,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa9bf6f81a1d0bada55358fd6bf1e7895cbfaf14","tid":645262,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"其實點解習種唔學金仔咁，乘機宣佈國共內戰正式結束，吞埋台積電，咁就一天都光晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:15:54.000Z","msg":"停戰簽和約相當於放棄台灣主權，唔再追求統一，咁仲吞咩台積電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebbcffb44bfdfbc5c66e8b6ae40ec8bfb4b27e4","tid":645262,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"台灣唔係屬於中國嘅一部分嘅咩？<br />\n點解可以向中國禁售<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a639b77672fbf106fc96b4ef5eb167b057c9295b","tid":645262,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7894845d570b63cae8b296fb04d57959e74e0e5","tid":645262,"uid":51620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:31:50.000Z","msg":"其實呢 成個中國嚟講得華為係有D料設計膠水CPU 啫係買人core 嘅圖紙再自己加野上去完成一粒CPU嘅圖<br />\n<br />\n中興呢D組裝廠就算鳩數啦<br />\n<br />\n但&quot;設計&quot;完 中國係冇晶片廠生產到所以都係要揾台電生產<br />\n<br />\n中國晶片廠良率好撚低 試過整左一餅出嚟 冇粒用得<br />\n<br />\n就算比佢整到出嚟 粒野效率都冇人地廠生產咁快<br />\n<br />\n所以<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/d/db/Jiangyoushutup.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20071122140305\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fdb%2FJiangyoushutup.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20071122140305&h=860cfba9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68f583c2596d46289eaae345e41fad918dfead79","tid":645262,"uid":96743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:34:45.000Z","msg":"台灣限售晶片給中興，中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"aa30a1b53cb37e1c72fd3dd4f0db8ed002ecda66","tid":645262,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:58:34.000Z","msg":"聯發仲唔趁機掠佢一筆，1千蚊1粒都要焗買<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe5c87d9d855d4d98ce45439c8464652fe6b9c9","tid":645262,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T00:46:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7286e390f0308fc6995e200d6b87c60099e990b8","tid":645262,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T01:14:32.000Z","msg":"經香港向台灣買又得唔得？"}]}